Reactions
<span>"Another death in Sicily. While we still weep the 5 missing workers in Casteldaccia this afternoon a young man lost his life rushing from a wind farm in Salemi, in the province of Trapani. But how can a family father come out of the house to earn bread and not return? That is enough, we must ensure the safety and safeguard of workers. The government is active immediately." It says the regional secretary of the Pd Sicilia, Anthony Barbagallo, in the afternoon in Castelvetrano with the secretariat Elly Schlein.</span>
